754→## Success Checklist
755→
756→Before considering database work complete:
757→
758→- ✅ Migration created with `npm run migrate:make`
759→- ✅ Migration follows pattern (transaction, logger, up/down)
760→- ✅ Table has _id, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at
761→- ✅ Appropriate indexes added
762→- ✅ Unique constraints use soft delete predicate
763→- ✅ Table name constant in @constants/db.constant
